name: UIImagePickerController.QualityType

items.name: case type640x480

items.name: case typeMedium
items.desc: If recording, specifies that you want to use medium-quality video recording.

items.name: case typeLow
items.desc: If recording, specifies that you want to use low-quality video recording.
